---
title: Pulled BBQ Jackfruit Burrito Bowl with Tomato Salsa & Sour Cream
description: You've heard of pulled pork, now we're bringing you an irresistible veggie version - pulled jackfruit marinated with mild chilli and
lime. And what better way to debut it than in a tried-and-true burrito bowl that requires no fussy assemblage – it’s straight in the
bowl and ready to jump into your mouth!
